[[Image:Latin dictionary.jpg|thumb|250px|A multi-volume Latin dictionary in the [[w:University Library of Graz|University Library of Graz]].]]

===Etymology===
{{etyl|ML.|en}} {{term|dictionarium|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|dictionarius|lang=la}}, from {{term|dictio||speaking|lang=la}}, from {{term|dictus|lang=la}}, perfect past participle of {{term/t|la|dƒ´c≈ç||speak}} + {{term|-arium||room, place|lang=la}}.

===Pronunciation===
