===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|encyclopaedia|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|·ºêŒ≥Œ∫œçŒ∫ŒªŒπŒøœÇ œÄŒ±ŒπŒ¥ŒµŒØŒ±||the circle of arts and sciences, curriculum|tr=enkuklios paideia|lang=grc}}, from {{term|·ºêŒ≥Œ∫œçŒ∫ŒªŒπŒøœÇ||circular, rounded, round|tr=enkuklios|lang=grc}}, from {{term|Œ∫œçŒ∫ŒªŒøœÇ||circle|tr=kuklos|lang=grc}} + {{term|œÄŒ±ŒπŒ¥ŒµŒØŒ±||the rearing of a child, education|tr=paideia|lang=grc}}, from {{term|œÄŒ±ŒπŒ¥ŒØŒøŒΩ||child|tr=paidion|lang=grc}}.

