===Verb===
{{af-verb}}

# {{non-gloss definition|Indicates that something is in a changing state}}
#: {{usex|lang=af|Ek het ryk '''geword'''.|t=I '''became''' rich.}}
#: {{usex|lang=af|Ek '''word''' ryk.|t=I '''am becoming''' rich.}}
#: {{usex|lang=af|Sy '''word''' beter.|t=She '''is getting''' better.}}
# {{non-gloss definition|Forms the present passive voice when followed by a past participle}}
#: {{usex|lang=af|Die kat '''word''' gevoer.|t=The cat '''is being''' fed.}}

